{
  "texts": [
    "As an example, stick-slip events can have a wide range of lengths and frequencies with documented durations from 0.1 to 1000 s and frequencies from 0.01 to 1000 Hz (see Podolskiy and Walter, 2016).",
    "Therefore, the parameters for the multi-STA/LTA algorithm recommended in Sect.",
    "S2.2b can be adjusted based on individual scenarios.",
    "We recommend a fresh grid search of parameters be considered, using the same approach to the parameter search described in Sect.",
    "S2.2b.4 (example codes via https://github.com/beccalatto/multi_sta_lta/), prior to implementation of the multi-STA/LTA in a new location."
  ]
}